description: Efforts to force a U-turn on the closure of two branches are at "the end of the road", an MHK says.
title: 'No hope' of U-turn on Isle of Man Bank branch closures
title_page: 'No hope' of U-turn on Isle of Man Bank branch closures - BBC News
maintext: A "significant proportion" of the bank's customers had already moved to digital banking and counter services at branches in other parts of the island would remain available to those who had not, he added.
